CITIZENTABLE_42161_126.description: Dr. Alexander Layendecker is the founder/Director of the Advanced SpaceLife Research Institute (ASRI). He completed a Master of Public Health (2013) and PhD in Human Sexuality (2016) from the Institute for Advanced Study of Human Sexuality, where his doctoral research focused on human sexuality and reproduction in off-Earth environments. He has been a featured speaker on popular podcasts such as The Space Show, The Space Revolution, and Age of Infinite, as well as at various conferences to include SXSW, ISDC, ASCEND, and New Worlds. His work has been featured in numerous academic publications and books to include A City on Mars, The Big Book of Mars, and Star Settlers: The Billionaires, Geniuses, and Crazed Visionaries Out to Conquer the Universe.

CITIZENTABLE_42161_126.description: Im Daniela Cisternas, a Chilean immigrant in Canada, Private Pilot, engineer, content creator, and analog astronaut crew. My passion lies in aviation and space exploration, and Im committed to using my platform to make these fields more accessible to diverse communities.  Through my immigrant journey, Ive built a community of 75K followers who see their own hopes reflected in my story. I inspire others to pursue their dreams, whether moving abroad, finding purpose, or achieving goals once thought impossible. If I can become a pilot and an analog astronaut, so can they.  Being an immigrant means living in-between: 50% from one place, 50% from another, and never fully enough in either. It takes resilience to adapt, but that in-betweenness is also a unique strength. I would be honored to represent this multicultural community, so that when I reach space, others who share my background can see themselves in me.
CITIZENTABLE_42161_126.name: Daniela Cisternas

CITIZENTABLE_42161_126.description: As Director of the Mars Society Canada, I have the privilege of helping humanity be prepared, scientifically, ethically, and culturally, for the responsibility of becoming a spacefaring species.   Thats why Ive founded programs like ASTRA, a national analog astronaut training program, the Space Health Division of Con.U, and the Canadian Space Exploration Conference (SPEX), all spaces where everyday dreamers can see their place in exploration. From flying 2 parabolic flights, exploring caves and multiple analog astronaut missions, I hope to inspire others through my Documentary to connect with this shared mission to the Moon and Mars.   As someone carrying on her shoulders multiple communities, Im grateful to have become someone others turn to for guidance and inspiration, carrying their hopes with me on this journey.    With your support at MoonDAO, I would be honored to bring our community along, and to accelerate progress towards Lunar and Martian settlements.

JOBBOARD_42161_115.description: Applications for our 2025 fellowship cohort are now open! Are you passionate about creating a sustainable and peaceful lunar future? Join our global fellowship program and contribute to groundbreaking research! As an Open Lunar fellow, you'll develop innovative lunar research projects while collaborating with leading experts in the space community. We welcome diverse backgrounds and unconventional thinkers. Learn more!
JOBBOARD_42161_115.title: 2025 Fellowship Program- Applications Open

JOBBOARD_42161_115.description: We are looking for a Director of Operations who is passionate about our mission and has a talent for strategic planning, program management, and operational leadership. This role is crucial to enhancing the efficiency of our operations and ensuring the successful execution of our initiatives. As the Director of Operations, you will be the backbone of our organization, managing the day-to-day execution of programs, financial oversight, legal compliance, and communications. Learn more!
JOBBOARD_42161_115.title: Director of Operations - Open Lunar Foundation

JOBBOARD_42161_115.description: LifeShip is building towards the launch of a DAO. Get in touch if you want to be one of the early members. We don't have paid positions at the moment. Compensation would be in tokens in the launch. LifeShip is a space society to preserve Earth and spread life to the stars. LifeShip's initial missions are monuments on the Moon with a backup of Earth. The vision builds towards a temple on the Moon and communities across Earth and space.
JOBBOARD_42161_115.title: Launch the LifeShip DAO

JOBBOARD_42161_115.description: LifeShip is looking for passionate individuals to drive business development, product sales, and commission-based B2B partnerships for our space-as-a-service offerings. LifeShip's is launching a series of monuments to the Moon as backups of Earths biodiversity, culture, and legacy. LifeShip has consumer products for people to send DNA, art, ashes, and more to the Moon. LifeShip has B2B partnerships with organizations wanting to send content to the Moon. Compensation in commission and equity.
JOBBOARD_42161_115.title: BD / Sales / Affiliates at LifeShip

JOBBOARD_42161_115.description: We are looking for a person to work on LunCo: D If you are: - want to contribute to Lunar Exploration, - have exp with Godot 4 3D, - Web3-native or web3-ready will to go full on crypto Jump on our Discord and say hi, maybe we could do something cool together
JOBBOARD_42161_115.title: Godot 4.4+ Dev

JOBBOARD_42161_115.description: We are looking for a person to shill LunCo & Decentralized Space Exploration on the Internet: If you are: - want to contribute to Lunar Exploration - have exp in marketing, particularly shilling on X Spaces - Web3-native or web3-ready will to go full on crypto Jump on our Discord to say hi, maybe we could build something cool together
JOBBOARD_42161_115.title: CMO/Shiller

Time Commitment & Compensation
Commitment: Up to 8 hours per week for 58 months (starting in January), depending on scope. 

Compensation: USD $35/hour

Location: Flexible and remote (Open Lunar operates globally; meetings often scheduled in Eastern Time Zone)

What Fellows Do
Research & Analysis
Investigate emerging ideas for peaceful lunar development

Draft background papers, reports, and articles

Develop annotated bibliographies and reading lists

Support research organization and synthesis

Collaboration
Participate in weekly fellowship calls with peers and staff

Present findings at research showcases and conferences

Engage with diverse stakeholders and incorporate feedback

Deliverables
Clear, concise outputs accessible to broad audiences

Provocative insights that drive new thinking in lunar governance

Final research presented as a published report, white paper, and community showcase

MARKETPLACE_42161_116.description: Show your pride in the Internet's Space Program with this exclusive MoonDAO logo t-shirt. Perfect for space enthusiasts and DAO pioneers alike, this shirt represents the future of decentralized space exploration. Join the movement that's taking humanity beyond Earth--one mission at a time!
MARKETPLACE_42161_116.title: MoonDAO Logo T-Shirt

MARKETPLACE_42161_116.description: Interested in launching your own DAO? Want help with the process of developing, funding, and operating a DAO? Book a 1 hour consultation with the MoonDAO core team to support your needs.
MARKETPLACE_42161_116.title: DAO Consulting

MARKETPLACE_42161_116.description: Realize your dreams of going to space and leave a legacy in the cosmos! With a LifeShip DNA kit, youll become part of a pioneering mission to expand humanity to the stars. Preserve your unique DNA on the Moon. Launch on a SpaceX rocket and watch live for the lunar landing. Youll receive a DNA collection kit, mission patch, and a digital certificate to commemorate your journey. Join a backup of Earth and send your DNA to the Moon.
MARKETPLACE_42161_116.title: LifeShip: Send your DNA to the Moon

MARKETPLACE_42161_116.description: Send your photo or artwork to the Moon with LifeShip, creating a unique and lasting lunar legacy! Your art will be UV printed in full color on a custom 1x1-inch aluminum layer and permanently preserved on the lunar surface. You'll receive two copies to keep on Earth, while one is sent to the Moon, allowing your vision to inspire future generations. Optional archival-grade Nickel NanoFiche or Ceramic for the highest resolution and durability are an added cost. Share your art with the universe!
MARKETPLACE_42161_116.title: Send a custom plaque to the Moon with your Art

MARKETPLACE_42161_116.description: Symbiont Labs believes that our relationship with technology should be expressed through multiple mediums beyond cybernetic implants. Here in fabric our substrate canvas becomes an invitation into deeper worlds of meaning transcending physical form. The Cultura Series is inspired by a unique fusion of pre-columbian futurism with reimagined cyberpunk twist in a collaboration with Honduran artisan and muralist Luis Vasquez.
MARKETPLACE_42161_116.title: Cultura Series V1-  Luxury T-Shirt

MARKETPLACE_42161_116.description: Are you interested in designing or commissioning a custom cybernetic implant?  Do you want expert help with the process of developing, funding, and operating a subdermal device? Book a 1 hour video consultation  and up an hour of background research with the Symbiont Labs team to support your needs. We're open to any project and budget but it all starts with a call.
MARKETPLACE_42161_116.title: Cybernetics Engineering / Prototyping  Consultation

See more examples at: graphicdesignanna.myportfolio.com
MARKETPLACE_42161_116.title: Mission Patch Design Service

MARKETPLACE_42161_116.description:
Commemorate your mission with a hand-painted acrylic painting on canvas.

Archival finish. 
Price based on 8x10 in canvas, shipping to North America

Contact graphicdesignanna@gmail.com to discuss.
MARKETPLACE_42161_116.title: Mission Painting - Fine Art on Canvas

MARKETPLACE_42161_116.description: Support the Advanced SpaceLife Research Institute and our research on human reproduction and sexuality factors in space by subscribing as an official ASRI network member! Annual Standard Membership Subscription includes: (1) ASRI Monthly Newsletter  stay up to date with on-going research efforts, events, conference presentations and key individuals involved in the fascinating study of sex in space! (2) Monthly discount codes for ASRI Online Store  new ASRI merchandise items added monthly! (3) Email updates/reminders regarding ASRI developments and upcoming member events  stay ahead of the crowd! (4) Access to members-only ASRI website portal  meet and network with other supporters, build your ASRI profile and community! (5) Access to member-exclusive ASRI social media content! *By purchasing this membership you agree to abide by ASRIs organizational Terms & Conditions of Service, Privacy Policy, and Subscription Member Code of Conduct as published, updated and maintained on our official website.
MARKETPLACE_42161_116.title: ASRI Annual Membership - Standard
